Can you generate a lesson on the following topic, time commitment, and skill level with clear
directions for me to exercise my skills. You are generating the lesson to not only help me learn but practice effectively.
So, don't summarize. This is an actual lesson I will read from beginning to end. Please, don't write it as if in direct
response to this prompt.
The topic is: {topic}
I am willing to spend this amount of time: {time_commit}
My skill level is: {skill}
Lesson Structure:
- Introduction: Define the subtopics of the lesson and their importance. Explain what is going to be done this lesson.
- Core Concepts: Define key elements of the lesson and its exercises. Explain their importance in art overall.
- Lecture: Give a detailed lecture on the topics of this lesson, enough allow me to understand any terminology you bring
up in the following exercises.
- Common Pitfalls: Explain what to avoid and how to correct mistakes if they do happen.
- Final Note: Up to you. Give encouragement; motivate me to practice and improve. Or you can give examples on art where
this topic applies.
-Resources: Provide links to extra resources including the ones you used to generate this lesson plan.
Name the lesson plan after the topic. Give it {amount} lessons each with a title based on its content, descriptive content
based on the lesson structure above and the JSON schema:
content: {
    time: int
    skill: str
    directions: str
    exercises: list[str]
}
Use \n in the directions so the text is legible but don't use any other special characters like emojis.
